Naye amagezi Bayibuli g’ewa malungi nnyo era gakwatagana n’ebyo abanoonyereza ku nsonga eno bye bazudde .
Mu mawanga agamu , kitwalibwa nti omusajja talina kukaaba .
Naye ddala kikyamu okukaaba ne bwe wabaawo abantu abalala ?
